Antonio Van Wyk’s Move to SV Ried: A Done Deal!
SV Guntamatic Ried has strengthened its offensive once again. In Austria, the transfer window closes today at 5 p.m. Antonio Van Wyk, a 22-year-old offensive player from Stellenbosch FC (South Africa), has signed in Ried, the OÖN reported.
